t actions and perceived US treaty violations. Ambiguity and mistrust now threaten another fragile understanding between them.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat/articleshow/132334422.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat/articleshow/132334422.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T22:12:31+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Chidanand Rajghatta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132334525,imgsize-944959.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['I bought a one-way ticket and moved back to India': Former H-1B visa holder says 'first time in my adult life I felt completely in control of my own career']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132334484.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/i-bought-a-one-way-ticket-and-moved-back-to-india-former-h-1b-visa-holder-says-first-time-in-my-adult-life-i-felt-completely-in-control-of-my-own-career/articleshow/132334484.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/i-bought-a-one-way-ticket-and-moved-back-to-india-former-h-1b-visa-holder-says-first-time-in-my-adult-life-i-felt-completely-in-control-of-my-own-career/articleshow/132334484.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T22:08:24+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132334498,imgsize-163744.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[6 killed as Russia rains missiles, drones on Ukraine; Kyiv renews plea for air defences]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132333773.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Recent missile and drone attacks from Russia have claimed the lives of six individuals and left many others wounded throughout Ukraine. In response to dwindling interceptor missile availability, Kyiv has made an emergency appeal for air defense systems. The strikes affected key locations, including Sumy, Odesa, Kharkiv, and Kyiv, with significant casualties in Sumy itself. While much of the aerial offensive was intercepted, ballistic missiles remained unchallenged.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/6-killed-as-russia-rains-missiles-drones-on-ukraine-kyiv-renews-plea-for-air-defences/articleshow/132333773.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/6-killed-as-russia-rains-missiles-drones-on-ukraine-kyiv-renews-plea-for-air-defences/articleshow/132333773.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T21:19:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132333795,imgsize-153716.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Explosive diarrhoea' parasite outbreak in US: Over 1000 cases reported in weeks, Michigan worst hit]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132333277.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/explosive-diarrhoea-parasite-outbreak-in-us-over-1000-cases-reported-in-weeks-michigan-worst-hit/articleshow/132333277.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/explosive-diarrhoea-parasite-outbreak-in-us-over-1000-cases-reported-in-weeks-michigan-worst-hit/articleshow/132333277.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T20:50:48+05:30</pubDate><dc:cr